text: Juan Carlos Martínez Camarena (born January 18, 1991 in Arandas, Jalisco) is a Mexican professional footballer who currently plays for Deportivo Marquense. He made his professional debut with Guadalajara during a Primera División draw against Querétaro on 17 March 2012. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican footballers Category:C.D.
